description:
It's time to get your kink on for Halloween!  We are hosting another Kinkology.

 

We regrettably must charge and entrance fee, please see the Kinkology group for information regarding the change in structure. 

In order to ensure entrance to Kinkology you must purchase tickets from and bring the printed ticket with you.  You must be 21 with a valid ID for admittance.......No exceptions. 

RSVPing on the event page alone will not ensure your admittance.  Navigate to for tickets.  Refunds will not be given after October 28th. 

As before, this will be a play party in a public venue possessing a liquor license, but will be CLOSED to the public.   Soooo.....we have some silly little rules to follow: 

We regret to inform all of our naked-loving friends....you must keep your naughty bits covered.  Pasties or electrical tape, up top over the nipples, and a thong down low. Keeps us legal.  Or, reverse them if you wish as long as the parts are covered. 

  • No intentional piercing or cutting of the skin.....Sadists....leave your knives and needles at home.
  • No vaginal or anal intercourse.
  • You must be 21
  • You must have a ticket


Now for the good stuff.........What we CAN offer:

  • A fully stocked cash bar
  • Jammin sounds to dance to or get lost in
  • Play stations with dungeon equipment for your sadistic or masochistic enjoyment
  • Photographs with permission of subjects....of course
  • And most of all.... a night of delicious kinky play with your friends to express your freedom of choice.


Please play responsibly and leave any drama or pissy attitudes elsewhere. 
 

Please drink responsibly and don’t drink and drive. Anyone traveling from out of town....there is a Holiday Inn Express (Asylum St), within walking distance, 2 blocks from the venue. 

Feel free to email KissableDom or Pinkmissive for any questions.  We can’t wait to see you!!!
